The discounts are not additive; it is impermissible to add the two discounts together. The appropriate discount is multiplicative. Assume PrivateCo is worth $4 million on an unadjusted basis (i.e., before applying discounts). Further assume a 25% minority interest discount and a 25% lack of marketability discount (LOMD) are appropriate. Exhibit 30.2 shows the application of the adjustments to PrivateCo's value.

